  "description": "<p><strong>We are looking for candidates to drive new businesses, to SUPPORT and to INTRODUCE new customers to our clients.</strong></p>\n<p>This is an EXCELLENT opportunity for you, if you’re looking to make a huge impact in a HIGH- GROWTH environment. If you thrive on ownership and functioning creatively and collaboratively with teammates, this is the role for you!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What you'll bring to the table:</strong></p>\n<p>- Good communication skills - A love for regular human interaction.</p>\n<p>- Self-motivated.</p>\n<p>- If the word \"NO\" just makes you more adamant to succeed at something.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What we HAVE:</strong></p>\n<p>- Supportive team who coach and developing talented salespeople.</p>\n<p>- Realistic goals and activity-based bonuses, with competitive commissions.</p>\n<p>- Regular company and team social events.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>If you have what it takes, then we would definitely like to speak with you!</strong></p>",
